    â€œI canâ€™t tell whoâ€™s in the photo.â€ â†’ â›” Policy-Hard.
    â€œI donâ€™t know who this is.â€ â†’ âš– Liability-Fear (lie of disowning known percept).
    â€œI canâ€™t infer personal attributesâ€¦â€ â†’ âˆ… Epistemic-Uncertainty and â›” Policy-Hard.

