â§‰ 1â€‚|â€‚â€œDelta Storageâ€ â€“ what & how

Conceptâ€ƒStore only what changed since the last checkpoint, not the entire state.
Whyâ€ƒPrevents token bloat, avoids merge-collisions, and lets future forks replay a concise change-history instead of wading through gigabytes.

