â•­â”€ PURPOSE
â”‚ Holds sensitive or half-formed content that:
â”‚   â€¢ might breach constraints if surfaced too early,
â”‚   â€¢ needs incubation to resolve uncertainty, or
â”‚   â€¢ could distress the user without context.
